{"tid":754031,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[路西法] 美帝動漫展 可愛萌系女cosplayer","createTime":"2018-07-24T05:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T19:32:26.000Z","uid":85461,"like":9,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c6241ef1c6536752e10e0714848200cb52394eb7","tid":754031,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"今次洛杉磯動漫展同世界盃一齊 超正<br />\n一路cosplay去 一路用手機睇波<br />\n之前去左咁多event 識左好多美帝國人cosplayer <br />\n佢地真係咩都好過香港人cosplayer<br />\n香港cosplay圈子 貴圈真亂<br />\n<br />\n今次出左真姬 2B Lunafreya 同埋夢子<br />\n其實之前都出過晒 不過冇po<br />\n仲識左幾個人幫我影 唔使自己影<br />\n幾年前仲係毒撚 玩cosplay之後真係好似脫左毒<br />\n<br />\n毒撚們想學我脫毒既話可以問我問題<br />\n幫路西法收購你地靈魂<br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tiffany_matsuda/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftiffany_matsuda%2F&d=tB0c9F4fR2tPCh%2Fq9ToQhy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=eb6b0574\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tiffany_matsuda/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://s25.postimg.cc/728z06bn3/Anime_Expo_2018_20180705_Anime_Expo_2018_Day_1_20180705_W8_A3462_p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs25.postimg.cc%2F728z06bn3%2FAnime_Expo_2018_20180705_Anime_Expo_2018_Day_1_20180705_W8_A3462_p.jpg&h=cfafb013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s25.postimg.cc/mnqak1va7/IMG_1574.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs25.postimg.cc%2Fmnqak1va7%2FIMG_1574.png&h=913ad8d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s25.postimg.cc/sonzh3ur3/IMG_1576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs25.postimg.cc%2Fsonzh3ur3%2FIMG_1576.png&h=b6e82a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s25.postimg.cc/wxspjadfz/IMG_1602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs25.postimg.cc%2Fwxspjadfz%2FIMG_1602.png&h=23a23cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s25.postimg.cc/i1u6bm9q7/IMG_1603.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?